OL,6,FWhen asked by Deputy Inna Gardiner in
OL,7,Fa written question whether there would
OL,8,Fbe government funding for further
OL,9,Fimprovements to the park,
OL,10,FInfrastructure Minister Andy Jehan
OL,11,Fsaid: "In 2024, #310k was allocated
OL,12,Ffor capital improvements to the
OL,13,FPavilion, covering enhancements to
OL,14,Fwelfare facilities and floodlight
OL,15,Finstallations.
OL,17,F"Additionally, a revenue budget of
OL,18,F#9,500 is in place for the facility's
OL,19,Foperational needs."
