OL,6,FThe minister was also asked whether
OL,7,Fthere would be extra safety signs.
OL,9,FDeputy Jehan explained existing
OL,10,Finformation boards in the park already
OL,11,Fgo beyond official guidance and that
OL,12,Fprotective equipment such as helmets
OL,13,Fand wrist guards are "strongly
OL,14,Frecommended".
OL,16,FHe added: "The skatepark is not
OL,17,Fsupervised so as operators we are
OL,18,Funable to enforce the wearing of
OL,19,Fhelmets, but it's important to note
OL,20,Fthat the majority of users choose to
OL,21,Fwear helmets."
